title: Smoky Bears win Region Championship
text:
Smoky Bears win Region Championship Updated: Fri 12:15 AM, Oct 23, 2015 / Headlines List / Article 
Sevierville,TN.--(WVLT) Head coach Tony Linginfelter and his Sevier County Smoky Bears win the Region 1-5A Championship by defeating Morristown West on rivalry Thursday football, 35-21.Vandy commit and Sevier County quarterback Deuce Wallace threw 4 touchdown passes in the win for the Smoky Bears who are the first team to score more than 14 points on the Trojans this season..
